        {
            "title": "A股半日偏軟   億華通升停   養殖股受捧",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日偏軟，深股跌逾1%，兩市合計成交10229億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指半日收報3357點，跌14點或0.44%，今早以3371點開市，跌不足1點或0.02%，最高見3377，升6點或0.18%，為半日高位，其後反覆向下，10:30AM後低見3359，跌12點或0.36%，半日成交3983.67億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日跌110點或1.02%，報10732點，今早開市報10830點，跌13點或0.12%。高見10865點，升22點或0.2%，隨即向下，最低見10747，跌96點或0.89%，半日成交6245.34億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數半日報3918點，跌6點或0.21%，今早開跌1點或0.04%，開報3925點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日報 2169，跌21點或0.99%，今早開市報2189點，跌1點或0.08%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">億華通A股(688339.SH)漲停，收升10.73%，報26.83元，旭陽集團(01907)入主成為北京億華通控股股東，北京億華通實際控制人變更為旭陽集團實際控制人，將發展氫能業務。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">養殖業升幅靠前，民和股份(002234.SZ)漲停，收升10.06%，報9.19元 ; 益生股份(002458.SZ)升3.33%，報9.01元 ; 曉鳴股份(300967.SZ)升2.3%，報13.35元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14772881-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e5%84%84%e8%8f%af%e9%80%9a%e5%8d%87%e5%81%9c-%e9%a4%8a%e6%ae%96%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%97%e6%8d%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A%E8%82%A1_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 11:45:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
